  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #1e90ff;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Mbox notice.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/40px-Mbox_notice.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/60px-Mbox_notice.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/Mbox_notice.png/80px-Mbox_notice.png 2x\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Note:</b> The title of this article is conjecture and may be subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> This article or section is a <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stub\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Stub\">stub</a>. You can help \"A Wiki Of Ice And Fire\" by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Lickspittle_lords&amp;action=edit\">expanding it</a> and/or improving existing text.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Late in the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a>, two factions arose at the royal court, the younger men that supported Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar Targaryen</a> and those that gathered around the king, whom <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Yandel\" title=\"Yandel\">Yandel</a> dubs <b><a href=\"/index.php/Lickspittle\" title=\"Lickspittle\">lickspittle</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lords</a></b> in his work <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_and_Fire_(Yandel)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The World of Ice and Fire (Yandel)\">The World of Ice and Fire</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf51.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf51.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_lickspittle_lords\">Known lickspittle lords</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lickspittle_lords&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known lickspittle lords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Owen_Merryweather\" title=\"Owen Merryweather\">Owen Merryweather</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Longtable\" title=\"Lord of Longtable\">Lord of Longtable</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/281_AC\" title=\"281 AC\">281&#160;AC</a> when Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a> resigned, removed from office shorty after <a href=\"/index.php/Robert%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rebellion\">Robert's Rebellion</a> began.</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Qarlton_Chelsted\" title=\"Qarlton Chelsted\">Qarlton Chelsted</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_coin\" title=\"Master of coin\">master of coin</a> and later named King's Hand, after Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a> is stripped of the office.</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lucerys_Velaryon_(master_of_ships)\" title=\"Lucerys Velaryon (master of ships)\">Lucerys Velaryon</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Tides\" title=\"Lord of the Tides\">Lord of the Tides</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_ships\" title=\"Master of ships\">master of ships</a>.</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Symond_Staunton\" title=\"Symond Staunton\">Symond Staunton</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_Rook%27s_Rest&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Lord of Rook&#39;s Rest (page does not exist)\">Lord of Rook's Rest</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_laws\" title=\"Master of laws\">master of laws</a>.</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Rykker_(lickspittle_lord)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Lord Rykker (lickspittle lord) (page does not exist)\">Rykker</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Duskendale\" title=\"Lord of Duskendale\">Lord of Duskendale</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Varys\" title=\"Varys\">Varys</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_whisperers\" title=\"Master of whisperers\">master of whisperers</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wisdom\" title=\"Wisdom\">Wisdom</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Rossart\" title=\"Rossart\">Rossart</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Grand_master\" title=\"Grand master\">grand master</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Alchemists%27_Guild\" title=\"Alchemists&#39; Guild\">Alchemists' Guild</a> and King's Hand after Lord Chelsted's execution.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lickspittle_lords&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf51.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf51.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Fall of the Dragons&#58; The Year of the False Spring.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Political_factions\" title=\"Template:Political factions\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Political_factions&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Political factions (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Political_factions&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nPolitical factions</div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">Blacks</a> (Rhaenyra Targaryen)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/in